ActBudget Implementation Act, 2018, No. 1
SubjectOrder Fixing April 30, 2021 and April 30, 2020 as the Days on which Certain Provisions of that Act Come into Force
PrecisOrder Fixing (1) April 30, 2021 as the day on which Division 2 of Part 6 of the BUDGET IMPLEMENTATION ACT, 2018, NO. 1 other than section 203, subsection 204(2), section 206 and subsections 211(1) and (3) to (5); and (2) April 30, 2020 as the day on which section 203, subsection 204(2), section 206 and subsections 211(1) and (3) to (5) of the Budget Implementation Act, 2018, No. 1, chapter 12 of the Statutes of Canada, 2018, COME INTO FORCE.
